│ │   NAVI AI       │ │                       │ │ Investor      │ │
│ │   - Damage      │ │                       │ │ Platform      │ │
│ │     Detection   │ │                       │ │ - Web3 Wallet │ │
│ │   - Cost Est.   │ │                       │ │ - Dashboard   │ │
│ │   - Recommend.  │ │                       │ │ - Portfolio   │ │
│ └─────────────────┘ │                       │ └───────────────┘ │
│                     │                       │                   │
│ ┌─────────────────┐ │                       │ ┌───────────────┐ │
│ │ NAVI Points     │ │                       │ │ STO Market    │ │
│ │ Database        │ │                       │ │ - Trading     │ │
│ │                 │ │                       │ │ - Liquidity   │ │
│ │                 │ │                       │ │ - Orders      │ │
│ └─────────────────┘ │                       │ └───────────────┘ │
└─────────────────────┴───────────────────────┴───────────────────┘
```

### Integration Workflow

#### 1. Fundraising Campaign Flow
```
NAVI AI (Damage Detection) 
    ↓ [API Call: Campaign Request]
NAVI Blockchain (Campaign Creation)
    ↓ [Smart Contract: Fundraising]
Investor Platform (Investment Interface)
    ↓ [STO Minting]
STO Marketplace (Token Trading)
```

#### 2. Points-to-Coin Exchange Flow
```
NAVI Doc (User Points Balance)
    ↓ [API Call: Exchange Request]
API Integration Layer (Rate Calculation)
    ↓ [Blockchain Transaction]
NAVI Blockchain (Navicoin Minting)
    ↓ [Wallet Update]
User Wallet (Navicoin Balance)
```

#### 3. Investment Return Flow
```
Ship Owner (Installment Payment)
    ↓ [Smart Contract: Payment Processing]
NAVI Blockchain (Distribution Calculation)
    ↓ [STO Token Verification]
Investor Wallet (Return Distribution)
```

