## SPESIFIKASI PLATFORM BLOCKCHAIN

### NAVI Blockchain Mainnet

#### Consensus Mechanism
- **Algorithm**: Delegated Proof of Stake (DPOS)
- **Validator Configuration**: 13 nodes (7 physical + 6 cloud distributed)
- **Block Time**: 3-5 seconds with instant finality
- **Transaction Throughput**: >1000 TPS
- **Network Uptime Target**: 99.9% availability

#### Physical Validator Specifications
**Hardware Requirements per Node:**
- **CPU**: AMD Ryzen 9 5950X / Intel i9-12900K (16+ cores)
- **Memory**: 64GB DDR4 3200MHz
- **Storage**: 2TB NVMe SSD + 4TB HDD backup
- **Network**: Dedicated 1Gbps dengan 99.9% uptime SLA
- **Power**: UPS backup system dengan RAID 1 configuration

#### Cloud Validator Specifications
- **Instance**: AWS c5.2xlarge equivalent
- **vCPU**: 8 cores minimum
- **Memory**: 32GB RAM
- **Storage**: 1TB NVMe SSD dengan automated backup
- **Distribution**: Multi-region deployment untuk redundancy

### Smart Contract Architecture

#### Core Contracts

**1. Fundraising Contract**
```solidity
contract NaviFundraising {
    struct Campaign {
        string campaignId;
        address shipOwner;
        uint256 targetAmount;
        uint256 currentAmount;
        uint256 deadline;
        CampaignStatus status;
        string[] milestones;
    }
    
    function createCampaign(
        string memory _campaignId,
        uint256 _targetAmount,
        uint256 _duration,
        string[] memory _milestones
    ) external;
    
    function invest(string memory _campaignId, uint256 _amount) external;
    function releaseFunds(string memory _campaignId, uint256 _milestone) external;
}
```

**2. STO Token Contract**
```solidity
contract NaviSTO {
    struct STOToken {
        string campaignId;
        uint256 totalSupply;
        uint256 dividendPerToken;
        mapping(address => uint256) balances;
    }
    
    function mintSTO(
        address _investor,
        string memory _campaignId,
        uint256 _amount
    ) external returns (uint256 tokenId);
    
    function distributeDividends(string memory _campaignId) external;
    function transferSTO(address _to, uint256 _tokenId, uint256 _amount) external;
}
```

**3. Navicoin Utility Contract**
```solidity
contract Navicoin {
    mapping(address => uint256) private _balances;
    
    function mint(address _to, uint256 _amount) external onlyMinter;
    function burnForFee(address _from, uint256 _amount) external onlyFeeCollector;
    function exchangeFromPoints(address _user, uint256 _points) external;
}
```

### Technology Stack

#### Blockchain Layer
- **Core**: Custom DPOS implementation in Go/Rust
- **EVM Compatibility**: Solidity smart contracts support
- **Storage**: IPFS integration untuk document storage
- **Bridge**: Multi-chain bridge to Ethereum, BSC, Polygon

#### Backend Infrastructure
- **API Framework**: Node.js dengan Express/NestJS
- **Database**: PostgreSQL untuk relational data, Redis untuk caching
- **Message Queue**: RabbitMQ untuk async processing
- **Authentication**: JWT dengan Web3 signature verification

#### Frontend Applications
- **Investor Platform**: React.js dengan TypeScript
- **Admin Interface**: React Admin dengan role-based access
- **Web3 Integration**: ethers.js untuk wallet connection
- **Mobile Support**: Progressive Web App (PWA) implementation

